name: Miao's Mission: Cat Food Frenzy!
description:
You are Miao, an alien traveling for the sole purpose of feeding your cats. On your journey however, your cat food is scattered across various planets. By dragging and dropping various cats to serve as platforms, you must reclaim the food you lost. Each cat behaves differently however, and you must use each of their unique properties to get to the goal. Go Miao, Go!
